data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 5 bedroom, 2795 square foot lovely home, with spacious floor plan, high ceilings, office/study and primary bedroom located downstairs, giving you the desired sanctuary for working at home, rest, relaxation, peace of mind and quiet. The Kitchen is beautifully and seamlessly connected to the dining and living room areas. The Gameroom which serves as a private family room or play area is located upstairs with the additional 4 bedrooms with Walkin closets to accommodate family members and guests, thereby making this a 5 bedroom lovely, prestigious and beautiful home.  The backyard of this home is very spacious offering a play and perfect place for entertaining your guests and family. Come and see. this home is located in the desirable neighborhood of the ENCLVE AT WESTOVER HILLS, with easy access to top rated schools, shopping malls, restaurants, with close proximity to the Sea World, Lackland Airforce base, Medical Center, Hospitals, and the new VA Hospital. This neighborhood is packaged with matured trees. Schedule your showings and fall in love with this home.
